Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.24,Title,SIGNS,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\pos(643.333,558)}Number 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.71,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Welcome to Haruka's Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:11.99,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,This program will introduce the friends that appear in Kotoura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:16.00,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I, Kotoura Haruka, will make the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.52,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Our guest for today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.64,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,is known as the "ESP researcher,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.00,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,and is the president of the ESP Research Society at Midorigaoka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.71,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Please welcome, Mifune Yuriko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.47,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I'm a second-year student at Midorigaoka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:32.92,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I'm Mifune Yuriko, the president of the ESP Research Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.42,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me here, Kotoura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:42.64,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I heard you're the founder of the ESP Research Society, President Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.28,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,What was the reason behind creating the ESP Research Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.75,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I did it because I wanted to study ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.60,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to meet a person who really has ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:56.60,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm glad I get to take part in the club activities as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:02.04,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,There are other people in this world who have ESP, just like you, Kotoura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:05.36,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are a few fakers among the bunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:11.52,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,but it's not right to label all ESPs as fakes because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:15.42,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Right. Um... By the way—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:20.66,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,If you {\i1}do{\i0} possess ESP, it's dangerous to display that ability in front of the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:25.53,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Since it's not a trick, there's no guarantee that the result will be what people expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:30.86,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,If you fail, you'll be shunned and treated like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:35.38,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,That is precisely why we need proper facilities for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.69,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,researching ESP and protecting those who have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:42.38,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Such government-run facilities exist in other countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:48.03,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I am forced to say that Japan is seriously lagging behind in the ESP research department!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:51.79,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,There are a few unofficial agencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.00,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Let's go to commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.49,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,but people with ESP—
